    "Kennel_Card_Website_Memo": "Meet Sully! Sully is a handsome 3-year-old with a smile so big it’s impossible not to smile back. The moment he sees a friendly face, that famous grin appears and his whole body lights up with excitement. This playful boy still has plenty of youthful energy and loves being part of the fun. Whether he’s greeting visitors with happy wiggles or leaning in for some well-earned pets, Sully’s joyful personality shines through in everything he does. More than anything, Sully loves his people. He’s a loyal companion who thrives on connection and attention, and he’s never met a staff member or volunteer he didn’t want to be friends with. If you’re looking for a fun-loving, handsome dog with a heart full of loyalty and a smile that can brighten your whole day, Sully is ready to meet you.",
