    "Kennel_Card_Website_Memo": "Rumpke is a big, beautiful boy with a gorgeous brindle coat that turns heads wherever he goes. And trust us—you’ll hear him before you see him! This vocal guy has the funniest little “piggy” sounds that make him impossible not to smile at. With his extra face folds and drooly enthusiasm (he’s a champion slobber shaker), Rumpke brings plenty of personality along with his good looks. But it’s not all silliness—Rumpke is ready for fun! He loves a good game of tug-of-war and is always up for an adventure. Whether it’s playtime or exploring the world by your side, he’s happiest when he’s engaged and active. If you’re looking for a playful, goofy, and lovable companion, Rumpke might just be your perfect match!",
