    "Kennel_Card_Website_Memo": "If you’re looking for energy… I’ve got plenty to share! I’m a one-year-old bundle of go, go, go, and I’m always ready for the next adventure. Sitting still? Not really my thing—I’d much rather be playing, running, or finding something fun to do with you. I haven’t quite mastered “calm” yet, but I make up for it with my excitement for life and my love for people. I’m looking for a friend who can keep up with me, enjoy some rough-and-tumble play, and help me burn off all this energy in the best ways. If you’re ready for an adventure buddy who will keep life exciting, I’m your guy!",
